!------------------------------------------------------------------------
!       Brief installation procedure
!------------------------------------------------------------------------
!

For detailed instllation procedure, please read documentation page 16--19.

The easiest way to install Calypso is the following:

0. Check options for configure 
    ./configure --help
1. Configuration
    ./configure [--prefix=/path]
2. Compile
    make
3. Install
    make install
4. Clean up objects
    make clean
5. To revert initial state of the repository, 
    make distclean 

For details of the configuration, type
./configure --help
